      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 4,
      "content": "Oh no, look how heavy the big green apple is! Because it has so much weight, it makes the whole board tilt down to one side. We must be careful when we play with things that weigh a lot.",
      "source_page_number": 4,
      "image": {
