      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 5,
      "content": "But wait, two small apples, one red and one pink, are perfectly balanced on the seesaw! This wonderful balance makes everyone feel happy because everything is just right. Look how sweet this perfect count is!",
      "source_page_number": 5,
